        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "[codex] feat(sandbox): support SecretRef docker env",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\n`sandbox.docker.env` previously accepted only literal strings. Operators who needed API keys, database URLs, or other credentials inside Docker sandbox containers had to put plaintext into `openclaw.json` or rely on ad-hoc environment interpolation outside the SecretRef flow. That left sandbox env credential handling inconsistent with model providers, skills, gateway auth, and other config-backed credential surfaces.\n\n## Summary\n\n- allow `agents.defaults.sandbox.docker.env.*` and `agents.list[].sandbox.docker.env.*` values to be SecretInput strings or structured SecretRefs\n- resolve active Docker sandbox env SecretRefs during runtime snapshot preparation while leaving inactive sandbox surfaces unresolved with diagnostics\n- include the sandbox Docker env targets in the direct `openclaw agent` command SecretRef detector and agent runtime target set\n- preserve existing literal Docker env string behavior exactly, including empty-string values like `FOO=`\n- register the new sandbox env credential surfaces for secrets plan/configure/audit and refresh the SecretRef credential docs matrix\n\nFixes #38309\n\n## Security Note\n\nResolved SecretRefs in `sandbox.docker.env` still become Docker container environment variables. That matches the existing Docker env behavior and keeps the docs warning that these values are visible through Docker daemon/container metadata; maintainer/security acceptance is still required for that boundary.\n\n## Evidence\n\nRedacted real Docker proof from this branch:\n\n```text\nagent target ids include sandbox env: agents.defaults.sandbox.docker.env.*, agents.list[].sandbox.docker.env.*\ncommand secret diagnostics: 1\nresolved config env string: true len=29 sha256=127866ee3204\nsandbox docker env normalized: true len=29 sha256=127866ee3204\nempty literal preserved: true\nsandbox container created: oc-sref-agent-main-f331f052\ncontainer env present=True len=29 sha256=127866ee3204 empty_literal=True\nsandbox container removed: oc-sref-agent-main-f331f052\n```\n\nValidation:\n\n- `node scripts/test-projects.mjs src/cli/command-secret-targets.test.ts src/commands/agent.runtime-config.test.ts src/secrets/runtime.test.ts src/secrets/runtime.coverage.test.ts src/config/config.sandbox-docker.test.ts src/agents/sandbox-merge.test.ts src/agents/sandbox-create-args.test.ts` passed: 5 Vitest shards, 177 tests total\n- `pnpm exec oxfmt --check --threads=1 ...` passed for touched files\n- `pnpm lint --threads=8` passed\n- `pnpm tsgo:core` passed\n- `pnpm tsgo:core:test` passed\n",
        "branch": "codex/38309-sandbox-env-secretref",
